<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA49">
<l>ceṟṟatuvuñ cērā viraṇiyaṉaic ceṉṟēṟṟup</l>
<l>peṟṟatuvu mānilam piṉṉaikkāy – muṟṟaṉ</l>
<l>muriyēṟṟiṉ muṉṉiṉṟu moympoḻittāy mūric</l>
<l>curiyēṟu caṅkiṉāy cūḻntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Going to the unapproachable Hiraṇya and destroying [him], receiving [water and]</l>
<l>obtaining the great earth [were yours]. For Piṉṉai’s sake, you obliterated</l>
<l>the strength of the bull, standing in front of [him, his] might ruined,</l>
<l>you with the great conch that rises with spirals all around.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
